Package: rSpotify
Type: Package
Title:  Access Spotify's API through R.
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2016-01-19
Author: Tad Dallas
Imports: devtools, igraph, jsonlite, RCurl, networkD3, testthat
Maintainer: Tad Dallas <tdallas@uga.edu>
Description: Constructs undirected graphs by querying the Spotify API. This allows you to do some cool visualizations of the relationships among artists, and just to explore what Spotify calls "similar artists".
License: GPL-3
